snippet.textDisplay: Wow. 0:45 Dr. Gotlieb says the cases that end up in pneumonia are 10-20%, and that you might need dozens of cases showing up in one city before you have enough cases concentrated at one institution in order to prompt for testing. I'm glad there are some professionals being heard that are taking this seriously enough to say we need to be extra cautious and proactive.
